1# Res > new > Android Resource Directory > 
	Resource type: font (this creat font repo.)

2# copy font from desktop, and paste to font repo.

3# Activity XML

	<TextView
		android : fontFamily="@font/fontname(all lower case.)" 

4# Google Fonts



5# Font_Family

	#1: FontFamily in xml
		1: Font Resource File
		*font repo > new > Font Resource File
		*File name: Font name
	
		2:   (1)font   (2)style   (3)fontWeight  [font weight android developer]

		*<font
			android: font="@font/fontName"
			android: fontStyle="normal"
			android: fontWeight="400"/>


	#2 Font_Family in Java:

		1: Typeface typeface = getResources().getFont( R.font.fontName ); / ResourcesCompat.getFont( this, R.font.fontName );

		2: onClickListener()
			TextViewID.setTypeface( typeface )
